The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | In the City
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     IN THE CITY
                  
	 BNR defeated Muslim Institute 3-1 in first division group A action of the BHA League on Wednesday. In another match, SAI Training Centre overcame BSF North Bengal by a solitary goal.      
	 In group B, Howrah Union and HTC Howrah drew 2-2. Sporting Union and Ranganathpur Union ended goalless.                
	 The fifth annual state physical training camp will be held at Salt Lake Stadium from Friday till April 24. More than 500 participants are expected.                
	HOCKEY: BHA League, first division group A: ERSA vs FCI (Mohun Bagan); BSF NB vs Khalsa Blues (CCFC). Matches from 3.30 pm.                                                                                                                                                                     
